verbose_text: Model B was based on model A and additionally adjusted for some behavioural habits and health related indicators of female partners including alcohol intake (yes/no), tobacco exposure (yes/no), BMI (underweight/normal/overweight/obesity), blood pressure (hypertension or no), genital tract infection (yes/no), HBV infection (yes/no), hemoglobin level (<115 g/L/> = 115 g/L/) and TSH level (decreased/normal/elevated).
